Package javax.resource

The javax.resource package is the top-level package for the Java EE Connector API specification.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Referenceable The Referenceable interface extends the javax.naming.Referenceable interface.
 

Exception Summary
NotSupportedException A NotSupportedException is thrown to indicate that callee (resource adapter or application server for system contracts) cannot execute an operation because the operation is not a supported feature.
ResourceException This is the root interface of the exception hierarchy defined for the Connector architecture.
